    <TD ALIGN='LEFT' COLSPAN='3' CLASS='header_stripe_TD'>
      Mrs. Seashore's Classroom!
    </TD>
  </TR>
</TABLE>
<B>
With Spring Break just around the corner, many of Mrs. Seashore's students have already started 
looking forward to the well-deserved rest that they'll get during their weeklong vacation.  
However, before making too many plans for Spring Break, her students will need to study harder 
than ever, since they're facing a very important set of exams right before their break.  Luckily, 
thanks to Mrs. Seashore's engaging and inspirational teaching methods, plus her use of educational 
games like <A HREF='http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=80'>Countdown</A>! and <A HREF='http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=12'>Solver</A>, even the most disinterested doodlers and daydreamers should have no 
problem getting their act together in time for exams!
